overlaps

public boolean overlaps(DateRange dateRange)
Compares this DateRange with another instance and validates that both overlap.
As an important note, having a null value in start or end date means that the range doesn't have a limit on that side.

Parameters:
dateRange - The DateRange with which compare this one.
Returns:
boolean true if both ranges overlap.
